Where to Watch

The pop singer, who was 11 years old when this 2001 concert was taped, performs in her home town of Glace Bay, Nova Scotia. Songs include "Driftwood," "Love So Rare," "The Island," "The Dance You Choose" and "Getting Dark Again."
